afterSignInUrl.description: Full URL or path to navigate after successful sign in.
afterSignInUrl.name: afterSignInUrl

afterSignUpUrl.description:
Full URL or path to navigate after successful sign up.
Sets the afterSignUpUrl if the "Sign up" link is clicked.
afterSignUpUrl.name: afterSignUpUrl

redirectUrl.description:
Full URL or path to navigate after successful sign in,
or sign up.

The same as setting afterSignInUrl and afterSignUpUrl
to the same value.
redirectUrl.name: redirectUrl
